translationBlock.key: Creates a merchant that can be traded with by players but is not attached to a physical entity. The ID given should not be a UUID. The title is the text that will display at the top of the window while a player is trading with it. Created merchants will persist across recompiles, but not across server restarts. An exception will be thrown if a merchant already exists using the given ID.
